3 Create your own function

## data is a matrix or data.frame
means_col <- function (data)
{
    n <- ncol (data)
    cmeans <- rep (NA, n)
    for (j in 1:n)
    {
        cmeans[j] <- mean (data[,j])
        
    }
    cmeans
}

## apply function
means_col (agpop[, 3:13])
